"12 ounces casarecce or fusilli pasta","1  (28-oz.) can diced tomatoes","2 cups chicken broth","1/2  medium-size yellow onion, sliced","4  garlic cloves, sliced","1 teaspoon dried oregano","1/3 cup firmly packed fresh basil leaves","2 teaspoons kosher salt","1 tablespoon olive oil","1/4 teaspoon dried crushed red pepper (optional)","1  (6-oz.) package baby spinach","  Freshly grated Parmesan cheese"